Change list:
- migration to Android SDK 28;
- migration to AndroidX;
- small changes in samples.

Thanks @TheJuki for [this Pull Request!](https://github.com/vivchar/RendererRecyclerViewAdapter/pull/25)

Change list:
- added new methods to ViewFinder;
- bug fixing;
- migration to 26 SDK;
- update Support Library to 27.0.2;
- update Build Tools to 27.0.3.

Change list:
* added most popular methods to ViewFinder;
* added Context to RendererRecyclerViewAdapter;
* added new Constructors without Context;
* added Deprecated signature to some Constructors;
* made DiffCallback.setItems public.

Change list:
* added CompositeViewBinder;
* added LoadMoreViewBinder.

Change list:
* added viewRecycled(ViewHolder holder) method to ViewRenderer;
* migration from RecyclerView.ViewHolder to internal ViewHolder;
* fix a critical issue related with ViewState.

Change list:
